    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>生物收集Roguelike卡牌构筑游戏。组建起拥有三只梦塔比的小队，智胜坏蛋，拯救城市！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141630/extras/ed8c0aba2ef293a86eb4db003d3dd38a.poster.avif?t=1764448571\" width=780 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141630/extras/ed8c0aba2ef293a86eb4db003d3dd38a.webm?t=1764448571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141630/extras/55308a2efab6bf0ec0b8c36620784d37.poster.avif?t=1764448571\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141630/extras/55308a2efab6bf0ec0b8c36620784d37.webm?t=1764448571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141630/extras/55308a2efab6bf0ec0b8c36620784d37.mp4?t=1764448571\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >构筑你的梦塔比队伍</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >要想当上大英雄拯救城市，手下就得有几只梦塔比！每只梦塔比都有一系列独特技能，为你和三人小队带来无限的战术选择与协同可能。收集道具，装备护符，规划成功之路！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141630/extras/0fd769591e4155e0f4ec97dae32ded74.poster.avif?t=1764448571\" width=780 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141630/extras/0fd769591e4155e0f4ec97dae32ded74.webm?t=1764448571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141630/extras/93110bb68727bf9b6bff879acdb11d6e.poster.avif?t=1764448571\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141630/extras/93110bb68727bf9b6bff879acdb11d6e.webm?t=1764448571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141630/extras/93110bb68727bf9b6bff879acdb11d6e.mp4?t=1764448571\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >进化并学习新技能</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >把你的梦塔比训练得更强，解锁新招式强化小队战略。通过升级，梦塔比会进化为更强的形态，获得全新卡牌能力，拓展你的战术选择。只要齐心协力，你和梦塔比定会无所不能！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141630/extras/89437119c6cd7fe32a723c143997ad8d.poster.avif?t=1764448571\" width=780 height=169 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141630/extras/89437119c6cd7fe32a723c143997ad8d.webm?t=1764448571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141630/extras/2b72b0ef9de49a3d265f3e266e902427.poster.avif?t=1764448571\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141630/extras/2b72b0ef9de49a3d265f3e266e902427.webm?t=1764448571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141630/extras/2b72b0ef9de49a3d265f3e266e902427.mp4?t=1764448571\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >智胜敌人</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >施展最佳策略，在独特的3x3网格战场里把敌人打得落花流水。每只梦塔比能力各异，因此你有无数选择，智取敌人，赢得胜利。不过要记得时不时在咖啡馆歇歇脚，恢复生命值！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141630/extras/c797d05bf8de5e5f854f54fca7dfec88.poster.avif?t=1764448571\" width=780 height=169 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141630/extras/c797d05bf8de5e5f854f54fca7dfec88.webm?t=1764448571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141630/extras/c65c1a513196816d47e0cc932bfef3de.poster.avif?t=1764448571\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141630/extras/c65c1a513196816d47e0cc932bfef3de.webm?t=1764448571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141630/extras/c65c1a513196816d47e0cc932bfef3de.mp4?t=1764448571\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >选择你的训练师</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从多样训练师中进行选择，每位都有独特玩法。你想把队伍部署到完美站位和敌人贴脸硬拼，还是用暖心餐食为梦塔比加把劲？城市面临危机，人人挺身而出！不过先要保证自身安全！训练师就像国际象棋中的王一样，如果被敌人打败，游戏就结束了。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >      </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141630/extras/990ae8e1e478a9c598e4c6fdeb340a5e.poster.avif?t=1764448571\" width=780 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141630/extras/990ae8e1e478a9c598e4c6fdeb340a5e.webm?t=1764448571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141630/extras/a2093d3f1e29559bcb1b7ef3388c666e.poster.avif?t=1764448571\" width=780 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141630/extras/a2093d3f1e29559bcb1b7ef3388c666e.webm?t=1764448571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141630/extras/a2093d3f1e29559bcb1b7ef3388c666e.mp4?t=1764448571\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >试试所有梦塔比</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们计划推出60多种梦塔比，每种都拥有独特而鲜明的玩法。选择你最爱的梦塔比吧！</p>",
